For __fresh kumquats__, the typical storage life is _3 Weeks_ in the fridge, whether sealed or not.

Title: Storage duration
Text:
For __fresh bagged greens such as leaf spinach and lettuce__, the typical storage life is _3–5 Days_ in the fridge, whether sealed or not, and _2 Days_ in the fridge if stored there after opening the package.

(Hints: Unopened product will last 3 - 5 days after date on bag, after opening it will last 2 days.)
